sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant B as Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis

    C->>B: POST /api/exams/:id/start
    B->>DB: Fetch exam
    B->>DB: Create session
    B-->>C: {sessionId, questions}

    loop Every 30s
        C->>B: POST /sessions/:id/answer
        B->>DB: Upsert answers
        B-->>C: {saved: true}
    end

    C->>B: POST /sessions/:id/submit
    B->>DB: Fetch all answers

    par Auto-grade L/R
        B->>B: Score listening
    and
        B->>B: Score reading
    end

    B->>DB: Update answer correctness
    B->>DB: Store L/R scores

    par Dispatch W/S
        B->>DB: Create W/S submissions
        B->>R: XADD writing task
        B->>R: XADD speaking task
    end

    B->>DB: Record L/R progress
    B->>DB: Set status=submitted
    B-->>C: {listeningScore, readingScore}
